These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, aquamarine, brown, turquise
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, azalea, poppy
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person who growspoppy is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsazalea##2
6. the person who likes turquise is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color   | turquise | lilac     | brown | aquamarine |
| Flower     | balloon-flower     | azalea | poppy  | daffodil      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, kiwi, grapefruit, apricot
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, lemonade, water
1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Food   | pomegranate | kiwi    | apricot     | grapefruit  |
| Beverage     | tea    | lemonade | coffee | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, whist, go
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse, paramedic, dressmaker
1. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
3. the paramedic is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
5. the paramedic is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Game   | billiard   | whist   | scrabble  | go |
| Job           | nurse | dressmaker | paramedic | entrepreneur  |

