.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, orange, brown
House: craftsman, modern, cottage, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes blood-red and the cottage house##2
3. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
4. the cottage house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Color         | mauve | blood-red | brown | orange  |
| House   | modern  | craftsman   | townhouse  | cottage |

