.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, guinea-pig, mouse
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, egyptian, french, pakistani
1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the polish is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
5. the pakistani is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Pet   | bird    | lizard   | guinea-pig | mouse    |
| Nationality      | egyptian | polish | french       | pakistani |

