.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, freelancer, project-manager, firefighter
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, february, october
1. the firefighter is on the right of the project-manager##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in october and the project-manager##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in february and the journalist##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
5. the freelancer is on the left or right of the firefighter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Job    | journalist | project-manager | firefighter | freelancer |
| Birthday   | august | may  | february    | october  |

