.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, snowboarding, lacrosse
City: rome, venice, san-francisco, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
5. the person traveling to venice is the person traveling to venice##1
6. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | volleyball | lacrosse | snowboarding | surfing     |
| City     | rome | paris  | venice   | san-francisco |

