4. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Color         | ivory | apricot | green | orange   |
| City   | berlin | venice | colone      | new-york |

