.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, disco, d&b
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, aconite, amaryllis
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of salsa is between the person who growsiris and the person who growsbegonia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre     | electronic | salsa   | disco      | d&b      |
| Flower   | iris     | aconite | begonia | amaryllis |

