.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, animation, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, badminton, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is rowing##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | disaster | animation      | western   |
| Sport   | badminton  | rowing    | ice-hockey | volleyball |

