3. the person watching sports movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
6. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| City       | hamburg | marseilles | berlin    | venice      |
| Movie-Genre   | action       | sports       | spy | disaster |

