.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, domino, snooker
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, asparagus, kale, lemon
1. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
6. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
7. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Game   | bridge | domino  | snooker | chess |
| Food           | kale     | lemon | lettuce    | asparagus     |

