.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, chess, billiard
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, gardening, photography, traveling
1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | domino | billiard  | chess      |
| Hobby    | traveling | video-games | photography | gardening |

