.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, horse
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, backgammon, go
1. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
6. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the cat##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Pet         | ferret | horse | lizard | cat |
| Game   | go     | monopoly       | scrabble   | backgammon      |

