.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, chinchilla, dog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, juice, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Pet   | frog | dog | chinchilla | ferret |
| Beverage         | coffee  | juice   | sprite | hot-chocolate     |

