3. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
4. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
5. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
