.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, pop, rock
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, nigerian, colombian
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of reggae is the colombian##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the fan of rock is on the far left or far right##3
5. the nigerian is between the fan of rock and the colombian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | pop | reggae  | salsa  | rock |
| Nationality           | chinese    | colombian | nigerian | dutch |

