.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, van, scooter
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, poker, bridge
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Transport   | scooter        | airplane       | van   | motorbike |
| Game    | bridge | poker | snooker | mah-jongg  |

