.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, time-travel, horror
4 different pets are kept: horse, rat, frog, bird
1. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the bird is the owner of the bird##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the horse is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | comedy     | time-travel          | horror |
| Pet      | horse | rat | bird | frog  |

 